We find that customers experience a lot of grief when it comes to contacting and asking for uupdates and invoices and whatnot from the organisation. The problem seems to be that the entire business is ran from a single cellphone.

SOLUTIONS

-SMS/Email Notification service to inform customers automatically about the progress of their vehicles
-Online Booking functionality to allow clients to book their car in for a service, at the comfortability of their homes.
